u.k. retail price rise 0.4 pct in februari the retail price index ( rpi ) , britain' measur of inflat , rose 0.4 pct in februari on a revis basi , to give a year-on-year rise of 3.9 pct , the employ depart said . in januari , the index rose 0.4 pct for a 3.9 pct year-on-year rise on both the previou base and the new index . the februari rpi wa set at 100.4 , base januari 1987. in februari 1986 , the rpi rose 0.4 pct , give a 5.1 pct year-on-year increas on the old basi . the inflat data compar with market forecast for a rise of 0.4 - 0.5 pct in februari and a yearli rise of about four pct , economist said . the employ depart said the rise in the index between januari and februari wa mainli the result of higher price for petrol , fresh veget , car and car mainten .